{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":1174,"text":"Hi."},{"time":2357,"text":"I want to talk about understanding,\nand the nature of understanding,"},{"time":6200,"text":"and what the essence of understanding is,"},{"time":9617,"text":"because understanding is something\nwe aim for, everyone."},{"time":12678,"text":"We want to understand things."},{"time":15763,"text":"My claim is that understanding has to do"},{"time":18135,"text":"with the ability to change\nyour perspective."},{"time":20737,"text":"If you don't have that,\nyou don't have understanding."},{"time":24106,"text":"So that is my claim."}]},{"cues":[{"time":25672,"text":"And I want to focus on mathematics."},{"time":28050,"text":"Many of us think of mathematics\nas addition, subtraction,"},{"time":31570,"text":"multiplication, division,"},{"time":33542,"text":"fractions, percent, geometry,\nalgebra -- all that stuff."},{"time":38034,"text":"But actually, I want to talk\nabout the essence of mathematics as well."},{"time":41732,"text":"And my claim is that mathematics\nhas to do with patterns."}]},{"cues":[{"time":45043,"text":"Behind me, you see a beautiful pattern,"},{"time":47558,"text":"and this pattern actually emerges\njust from drawing circles"},{"time":51513,"text":"in a very particular way."},{"time":53778,"text":"So my day-to-day definition\nof mathematics that I use every day"},{"time":58391,"text":"is the following:"},{"time":60030,"text":"First of all, it's about finding patterns."},{"time":64001,"text":"And by \"pattern,\" I mean a connection,\na structure, some regularity,"},{"time":69520,"text":"some rules that govern what we see."},{"time":72170,"text":"Second of all,"},{"time":73349,"text":"I think it is about representing\nthese patterns with a language."},{"time":77361,"text":"We make up language if we don't have it,"},{"time":79829,"text":"and in mathematics, this is essential."},{"time":83013,"text":"It's also about making assumptions"},{"time":84837,"text":"and playing around with these assumptions\nand just seeing what happens."},{"time":88474,"text":"We're going to do that very soon."},{"time":90986,"text":"And finally, it's about doing cool stuff."},{"time":94460,"text":"Mathematics enables us\nto do so many things."}]},{"cues":[{"time":98632,"text":"So let's have a look at these patterns."},{"time":100872,"text":"If you want to tie a tie knot,"},{"time":103118,"text":"there are patterns."},{"time":104452,"text":"Tie knots have names."},{"time":106453,"text":"And you can also do\nthe mathematics of tie knots."},{"time":108824,"text":"This is a left-out, right-in,\ncenter-out and tie."},{"time":112073,"text":"This is a left-in, right-out,\nleft-in, center-out and tie."},{"time":116005,"text":"This is a language we made up\nfor the patterns of tie knots,"},{"time":120522,"text":"and a half-Windsor is all that."},{"time":123529,"text":"This is a mathematics book\nabout tying shoelaces"},{"time":126340,"text":"at the university level,"},{"time":127754,"text":"because there are patterns in shoelaces."},{"time":129756,"text":"You can do it in so many different ways."},{"time":131891,"text":"We can analyze it."},{"time":133159,"text":"We can make up languages for it."}]},{"cues":[{"time":136218,"text":"And representations\nare all over mathematics."},{"time":139181,"text":"This is Leibniz's notation from 1675."},{"time":143335,"text":"He invented a language\nfor patterns in nature."},{"time":147363,"text":"When we throw something up in the air,"},{"time":149255,"text":"it falls down."},{"time":150469,"text":"Why?"},{"time":151644,"text":"We're not sure, but we can represent\nthis with mathematics in a pattern."}]},{"cues":[{"time":156285,"text":"This is also a pattern."},{"time":157912,"text":"This is also an invented language."},{"time":160636,"text":"Can you guess for what?"},{"time":163481,"text":"It is actually a notation system\nfor dancing, for tap dancing."},{"time":167532,"text":"That enables him as a choreographer\nto do cool stuff, to do new things,"},{"time":172812,"text":"because he has represented it."}]},{"cues":[{"time":175232,"text":"I want you to think about how amazing\nrepresenting something actually is."},{"time":180620,"text":"Here it says the word \"mathematics.\""},{"time":183905,"text":"But actually, they're just dots, right?"},{"time":186329,"text":"So how in the world can these dots\nrepresent the word?"},{"time":189344,"text":"Well, they do."},{"time":191343,"text":"They represent the word \"mathematics,\""},{"time":193265,"text":"and these symbols also represent that word"},{"time":195849,"text":"and this we can listen to."},{"time":197531,"text":"It sounds like this."}]},{"cues":[{"time":198912,"text":"(Beeps)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":200920,"text":"Somehow these sounds represent\nthe word and the concept."},{"time":204234,"text":"How does this happen?"},{"time":205914,"text":"There's something amazing\ngoing on about representing stuff."}]},{"cues":[{"time":209966,"text":"So I want to talk about\nthat magic that happens"},{"time":215607,"text":"when we actually represent something."},{"time":217602,"text":"Here you see just lines\nwith different widths."},{"time":220642,"text":"They stand for numbers\nfor a particular book."},{"time":223291,"text":"And I can actually recommend\nthis book, it's a very nice book."}]},{"cues":[{"time":226308,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":227354,"text":"Just trust me."}]},{"cues":[{"time":229475,"text":"OK, so let's just do an experiment,"},{"time":231822,"text":"just to play around\nwith some straight lines."},{"time":234014,"text":"This is a straight line."},{"time":235205,"text":"Let's make another one."},{"time":236383,"text":"So every time we move,\nwe move one down and one across,"},{"time":239216,"text":"and we draw a new straight line, right?"},{"time":241814,"text":"We do this over and over and over,"},{"time":244351,"text":"and we look for patterns."},{"time":245733,"text":"So this pattern emerges,"},{"time":248220,"text":"and it's a rather nice pattern."},{"time":250286,"text":"It looks like a curve, right?"},{"time":252045,"text":"Just from drawing simple, straight lines."}]},{"cues":[{"time":255271,"text":"Now I can change my perspective\na little bit. I can rotate it."},{"time":258944,"text":"Have a look at the curve."},{"time":260350,"text":"What does it look like?"},{"time":261753,"text":"Is it a part of a circle?"},{"time":263759,"text":"It's actually not a part of a circle."},{"time":265685,"text":"So I have to continue my investigation\nand look for the true pattern."},{"time":269868,"text":"Perhaps if I copy it and make some art?"},{"time":273674,"text":"Well, no."},{"time":274854,"text":"Perhaps I should extend\nthe lines like this,"},{"time":277027,"text":"and look for the pattern there."},{"time":278821,"text":"Let's make more lines."},{"time":280140,"text":"We do this."},{"time":281394,"text":"And then let's zoom out\nand change our perspective again."},{"time":285801,"text":"Then we can actually see that\nwhat started out as just straight lines"},{"time":289336,"text":"is actually a curve called a parabola."},{"time":291855,"text":"This is represented by a simple equation,"},{"time":295096,"text":"and it's a beautiful pattern."}]},{"cues":[{"time":297521,"text":"So this is the stuff that we do."},{"time":299320,"text":"We find patterns, and we represent them."},{"time":301954,"text":"And I think this is a nice\nday-to-day definition."},{"time":304602,"text":"But today I want to go\na little bit deeper,"},{"time":306957,"text":"and think about\nwhat the nature of this is."},{"time":310925,"text":"What makes it possible?"},{"time":312377,"text":"There's one thing\nthat's a little bit deeper,"},{"time":314555,"text":"and that has to do with the ability\nto change your perspective."},{"time":318082,"text":"And I claim that when\nyou change your perspective,"},{"time":320629,"text":"and if you take another point of view,"},{"time":323459,"text":"you learn something new\nabout what you are watching"},{"time":327393,"text":"or looking at or hearing."},{"time":329472,"text":"And I think this is a really important\nthing that we do all the time."}]},{"cues":[{"time":333834,"text":"So let's just look at\nthis simple equation,"},{"time":337838,"text":"x + x = 2 • x."},{"time":340411,"text":"This is a very nice pattern,\nand it's true,"},{"time":342507,"text":"because 5 + 5 = 2 • 5, etc."},{"time":345360,"text":"We've seen this over and over,\nand we represent it like this."},{"time":348485,"text":"But think about it: this is an equation."},{"time":351025,"text":"It says that something\nis equal to something else,"},{"time":353611,"text":"and that's two different perspectives."},{"time":355922,"text":"One perspective is, it's a sum."},{"time":357845,"text":"It's something you plus together."},{"time":359715,"text":"On the other hand, it's a multiplication,"},{"time":362111,"text":"and those are two different perspectives."},{"time":365140,"text":"And I would go as far as to say\nthat every equation is like this,"},{"time":368912,"text":"every mathematical equation\nwhere you use that equality sign"},{"time":373052,"text":"is actually a metaphor."},{"time":374919,"text":"It's an analogy between two things."},{"time":376949,"text":"You're just viewing something\nand taking two different points of view,"},{"time":380468,"text":"and you're expressing that in a language."}]},{"cues":[{"time":382885,"text":"Have a look at this equation."},{"time":384473,"text":"This is one of the most\nbeautiful equations."},{"time":386752,"text":"It simply says that, well,"},{"time":389902,"text":"two things, they're both -1."},{"time":392279,"text":"This thing on the left-hand side is -1,\nand the other one is."},{"time":395693,"text":"And that, I think, is one\nof the essential parts"},{"time":398043,"text":"of mathematics -- you take\ndifferent points of view."}]},{"cues":[{"time":400530,"text":"So let's just play around."},{"time":401889,"text":"Let's take a number."},{"time":403180,"text":"We know four-thirds.\nWe know what four-thirds is."},{"time":406082,"text":"It's 1.333, but we have to have\nthose three dots,"},{"time":409489,"text":"otherwise it's not exactly four-thirds."},{"time":411886,"text":"But this is only in base 10."},{"time":413806,"text":"You know, the number system,\nwe use 10 digits."},{"time":416093,"text":"If we change that around\nand only use two digits,"},{"time":418435,"text":"that's called the binary system."},{"time":420269,"text":"It's written like this."},{"time":421996,"text":"So we're now talking about the number."},{"time":423982,"text":"The number is four-thirds."},{"time":425964,"text":"We can write it like this,"},{"time":427331,"text":"and we can change the base,\nchange the number of digits,"},{"time":430360,"text":"and we can write it differently."}]},{"cues":[{"time":432172,"text":"So these are all representations\nof the same number."},{"time":436363,"text":"We can even write it simply,\nlike 1.3 or 1.6."},{"time":439935,"text":"It all depends on\nhow many digits you have."},{"time":442521,"text":"Or perhaps we just simplify\nand write it like this."},{"time":445927,"text":"I like this one, because this says\nfour divided by three."},{"time":449166,"text":"And this number expresses\na relation between two numbers."},{"time":452227,"text":"You have four on the one hand\nand three on the other."},{"time":455215,"text":"And you can visualize this in many ways."},{"time":457317,"text":"What I'm doing now is viewing that number\nfrom different perspectives."},{"time":461388,"text":"I'm playing around."},{"time":462563,"text":"I'm playing around with\nhow we view something,"},{"time":465131,"text":"and I'm doing it very deliberately."},{"time":466867,"text":"We can take a grid."},{"time":468074,"text":"If it's four across and three up,\nthis line equals five, always."},{"time":472776,"text":"It has to be like this.\nThis is a beautiful pattern."},{"time":475488,"text":"Four and three and five."},{"time":477177,"text":"And this rectangle, which is 4 x 3,"},{"time":479912,"text":"you've seen a lot of times."},{"time":481527,"text":"This is your average computer screen."},{"time":483364,"text":"800 x 600 or 1,600 x 1,200"},{"time":486767,"text":"is a television or a computer screen."}]},{"cues":[{"time":489864,"text":"So these are all nice representations,"},{"time":491920,"text":"but I want to go a little bit further\nand just play more with this number."},{"time":495866,"text":"Here you see two circles.\nI'm going to rotate them like this."},{"time":499138,"text":"Observe the upper-left one."},{"time":500950,"text":"It goes a little bit faster, right?"},{"time":503137,"text":"You can see this."},{"time":504319,"text":"It actually goes exactly\nfour-thirds as fast."},{"time":507717,"text":"That means that when it goes\naround four times,"},{"time":510141,"text":"the other one goes around three times."},{"time":512044,"text":"Now let's make two lines, and draw\nthis dot where the lines meet."},{"time":515569,"text":"We get this dot dancing around."}]},{"cues":[{"time":517295,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":518356,"text":"And this dot comes from that number."},{"time":520926,"text":"Right? Now we should trace it."},{"time":523239,"text":"Let's trace it and see what happens."},{"time":525441,"text":"This is what mathematics is all about."},{"time":527393,"text":"It's about seeing what happens."},{"time":529052,"text":"And this emerges from four-thirds."},{"time":532020,"text":"I like to say that this\nis the image of four-thirds."},{"time":535404,"text":"It's much nicer -- (Cheers)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":536724,"text":"Thank you!"}]},{"cues":[{"time":537906,"text":"(Applause)"},{"time":544556,"text":"This is not new."},{"time":545731,"text":"This has been known\nfor a long time, but --"}]},{"cues":[{"time":547789,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":549422,"text":"But this is four-thirds."}]},{"cues":[{"time":551130,"text":"Let's do another experiment."},{"time":552713,"text":"Let's now take a sound, this sound: (Beep)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":556846,"text":"This is a perfect A, 440Hz."},{"time":559859,"text":"Let's multiply it by two."},{"time":561569,"text":"We get this sound. (Beep)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":562952,"text":"When we play them together,\nit sounds like this."},{"time":565231,"text":"This is an octave, right?"},{"time":566468,"text":"We can do this game. We can play\na sound, play the same A."},{"time":569257,"text":"We can multiply it by three-halves."}]},{"cues":[{"time":570982,"text":"(Beep)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":572624,"text":"This is what we call a perfect fifth."}]},{"cues":[{"time":574592,"text":"(Beep)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":575662,"text":"They sound really nice together."},{"time":577792,"text":"Let's multiply this sound\nby four-thirds. (Beep)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":581939,"text":"What happens?"},{"time":583889,"text":"You get this sound. (Beep)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":585344,"text":"This is the perfect fourth."},{"time":586654,"text":"If the first one is an A, this is a D."},{"time":588923,"text":"They sound like this together. (Beeps)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":590977,"text":"This is the sound of four-thirds."},{"time":593411,"text":"What I'm doing now,\nI'm changing my perspective."},{"time":595989,"text":"I'm just viewing a number\nfrom another perspective."}]},{"cues":[{"time":598793,"text":"I can even do this with rhythms, right?"},{"time":600782,"text":"I can take a rhythm and play\nthree beats at one time (Drumbeats)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":604478,"text":"in a period of time,"},{"time":606053,"text":"and I can play another sound\nfour times in that same space."}]},{"cues":[{"time":610419,"text":"(Clanking sounds)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":611485,"text":"Sounds kind of boring,\nbut listen to them together."}]},{"cues":[{"time":613890,"text":"(Drumbeats and clanking sounds)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":616700,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":618014,"text":"Hey! So."}]},{"cues":[{"time":619459,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":621371,"text":"I can even make a little hi-hat."}]},{"cues":[{"time":623554,"text":"(Drumbeats and cymbals)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":625419,"text":"Can you hear this?"},{"time":626594,"text":"So, this is the sound of four-thirds."},{"time":628731,"text":"Again, this is as a rhythm."}]},{"cues":[{"time":630605,"text":"(Drumbeats and cowbell)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":632439,"text":"And I can keep doing this\nand play games with this number."},{"time":635311,"text":"Four-thirds is a really great number.\nI love four-thirds!"}]},{"cues":[{"time":638080,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":639380,"text":"Truly -- it's an undervalued number."},{"time":641891,"text":"So if you take a sphere and look\nat the volume of the sphere,"},{"time":644774,"text":"it's actually four-thirds\nof some particular cylinder."},{"time":647731,"text":"So four-thirds is in the sphere.\nIt's the volume of the sphere."}]},{"cues":[{"time":651824,"text":"OK, so why am I doing all this?"},{"time":653890,"text":"Well, I want to talk about what it means\nto understand something"},{"time":657144,"text":"and what we mean\nby understanding something."},{"time":659732,"text":"That's my aim here."},{"time":661179,"text":"And my claim is that\nyou understand something"},{"time":663333,"text":"if you have the ability to view it\nfrom different perspectives."},{"time":666349,"text":"Let's look at this letter.\nIt's a beautiful R, right?"},{"time":668914,"text":"How do you know that?"},{"time":670557,"text":"Well, as a matter of fact,\nyou've seen a bunch of R's,"},{"time":673769,"text":"and you've generalized"},{"time":675438,"text":"and abstracted all of these\nand found a pattern."},{"time":678432,"text":"So you know that this is an R."}]},{"cues":[{"time":683643,"text":"So what I'm aiming for here\nis saying something"},{"time":686474,"text":"about how understanding\nand changing your perspective"},{"time":689879,"text":"are linked."},{"time":691235,"text":"And I'm a teacher and a lecturer,"},{"time":693428,"text":"and I can actually use this\nto teach something,"},{"time":695764,"text":"because when I give someone else\nanother story, a metaphor, an analogy,"},{"time":700628,"text":"if I tell a story\nfrom a different point of view,"},{"time":703051,"text":"I enable understanding."},{"time":704588,"text":"I make understanding possible,"},{"time":706478,"text":"because you have to generalize\nover everything you see and hear,"},{"time":709568,"text":"and if I give you another perspective,\nthat will become easier for you."}]},{"cues":[{"time":714191,"text":"Let's do a simple example again."},{"time":716121,"text":"This is four and three.\nThis is four triangles."},{"time":718786,"text":"So this is also four-thirds, in a way."},{"time":721258,"text":"Let's just join them together."},{"time":723004,"text":"Now we're going to play a game;\nwe're going to fold it up"},{"time":725737,"text":"into a three-dimensional structure."},{"time":727443,"text":"I love this."},{"time":728631,"text":"This is a square pyramid."},{"time":730529,"text":"And let's just take two of them\nand put them together."},{"time":733703,"text":"So this is what is called an octahedron."},{"time":736416,"text":"It's one of the five platonic solids."},{"time":739147,"text":"Now we can quite literally\nchange our perspective,"},{"time":741616,"text":"because we can rotate it\naround all of the axes"},{"time":744335,"text":"and view it from different perspectives."},{"time":746371,"text":"And I can change the axis,"},{"time":748461,"text":"and then I can view it\nfrom another point of view,"},{"time":750823,"text":"but it's the same thing,\nbut it looks a little different."},{"time":753550,"text":"I can do it even one more time."}]},{"cues":[{"time":755242,"text":"Every time I do this,\nsomething else appears,"},{"time":758568,"text":"so I'm actually learning\nmore about the object"},{"time":760771,"text":"when I change my perspective."},{"time":762320,"text":"I can use this as a tool\nfor creating understanding."},{"time":766548,"text":"I can take two of these\nand put them together like this"},{"time":770164,"text":"and see what happens."},{"time":771865,"text":"And it looks a little bit\nlike the octahedron."},{"time":775300,"text":"Have a look at it if I spin\nit around like this."},{"time":777802,"text":"What happens?"},{"time":779008,"text":"Well, if you take two of these,\njoin them together and spin it around,"},{"time":782376,"text":"there's your octahedron again,"},{"time":784801,"text":"a beautiful structure."},{"time":786456,"text":"If you lay it out flat on the floor,"},{"time":788644,"text":"this is the octahedron."},{"time":789885,"text":"This is the graph structure\nof an octahedron."},{"time":793255,"text":"And I can continue doing this."},{"time":795652,"text":"You can draw three great circles\naround the octahedron,"},{"time":799203,"text":"and you rotate around,"},{"time":801077,"text":"so actually three great circles\nis related to the octahedron."},{"time":805562,"text":"And if I take a bicycle pump\nand just pump it up,"},{"time":809245,"text":"you can see that this is also\na little bit like the octahedron."},{"time":812801,"text":"Do you see what I'm doing here?"},{"time":815121,"text":"I am changing the perspective every time."}]},{"cues":[{"time":818801,"text":"So let's now take a step back --"},{"time":821475,"text":"and that's actually\na metaphor, stepping back --"},{"time":824536,"text":"and have a look at what we're doing."},{"time":826923,"text":"I'm playing around with metaphors."},{"time":828611,"text":"I'm playing around\nwith perspectives and analogies."},{"time":831107,"text":"I'm telling one story in different ways."},{"time":833472,"text":"I'm telling stories."},{"time":834706,"text":"I'm making a narrative;\nI'm making several narratives."},{"time":837914,"text":"And I think all of these things\nmake understanding possible."},{"time":841460,"text":"I think this actually is the essence\nof understanding something."},{"time":844863,"text":"I truly believe this."}]},{"cues":[{"time":846181,"text":"So this thing about changing\nyour perspective --"},{"time":848608,"text":"it's absolutely fundamental for humans."},{"time":851829,"text":"Let's play around with the Earth."},{"time":853474,"text":"Let's zoom into the ocean,\nhave a look at the ocean."},{"time":856007,"text":"We can do this with anything."},{"time":857973,"text":"We can take the ocean\nand view it up close."},{"time":860457,"text":"We can look at the waves."},{"time":862415,"text":"We can go to the beach."},{"time":863651,"text":"We can view the ocean\nfrom another perspective."},{"time":865938,"text":"Every time we do this, we learn\na little bit more about the ocean."},{"time":869152,"text":"If we go to the shore,\nwe can kind of smell it, right?"},{"time":871765,"text":"We can hear the sound of the waves."},{"time":873499,"text":"We can feel salt on our tongues."},{"time":875569,"text":"So all of these\nare different perspectives."},{"time":878483,"text":"And this is the best one."},{"time":879771,"text":"We can go into the water."},{"time":881438,"text":"We can see the water from the inside."},{"time":883471,"text":"And you know what?"},{"time":884673,"text":"This is absolutely essential\nin mathematics and computer science."},{"time":887778,"text":"If you're able to view\na structure from the inside,"},{"time":890757,"text":"then you really learn something about it."},{"time":893351,"text":"That's somehow the essence of something."}]},{"cues":[{"time":895883,"text":"So when we do this,\nand we've taken this journey"},{"time":899550,"text":"into the ocean,"},{"time":900747,"text":"we use our imagination."},{"time":902661,"text":"And I think this is one level deeper,"},{"time":905338,"text":"and it's actually a requirement\nfor changing your perspective."},{"time":909818,"text":"We can do a little game."},{"time":911009,"text":"You can imagine that you're sitting there."},{"time":913074,"text":"You can imagine that you're up here,\nand that you're sitting here."},{"time":916325,"text":"You can view yourselves from the outside."},{"time":918675,"text":"That's really a strange thing."},{"time":920637,"text":"You're changing your perspective."},{"time":922484,"text":"You're using your imagination,"},{"time":924367,"text":"and you're viewing yourself\nfrom the outside."},{"time":927073,"text":"That requires imagination."}]},{"cues":[{"time":929126,"text":"Mathematics and computer science\nare the most imaginative art forms ever."},{"time":934884,"text":"And this thing about changing perspectives"},{"time":937090,"text":"should sound a little bit familiar to you,"},{"time":939622,"text":"because we do it every day."},{"time":942604,"text":"And then it's called empathy."},{"time":944954,"text":"When I view the world\nfrom your perspective,"},{"time":948939,"text":"I have empathy with you."},{"time":950629,"text":"If I really, truly understand"},{"time":952501,"text":"what the world looks\nlike from your perspective,"},{"time":955603,"text":"I am empathetic."},{"time":957098,"text":"That requires imagination."},{"time":959827,"text":"And that is how we obtain understanding."},{"time":963206,"text":"And this is all over mathematics\nand this is all over computer science,"},{"time":966983,"text":"and there's a really deep connection\nbetween empathy and these sciences."}]},{"cues":[{"time":973288,"text":"So my conclusion is the following:"},{"time":977931,"text":"understanding something really deeply"},{"time":980177,"text":"has to do with the ability\nto change your perspective."},{"time":983894,"text":"So my advice to you is:\ntry to change your perspective."},{"time":987507,"text":"You can study mathematics."},{"time":989080,"text":"It's a wonderful way to train your brain."},{"time":992663,"text":"Changing your perspective\nmakes your mind more flexible."},{"time":996495,"text":"It makes you open to new things,"},{"time":998353,"text":"and it makes you\nable to understand things."},{"time":1001202,"text":"And to use yet another metaphor:"},{"time":1003243,"text":"have a mind like water."},{"time":1004748,"text":"That's nice."}]},{"cues":[{"time":1005923,"text":"Thank you."}]},{"cues":[{"time":1007104,"text":"(Applause)"}]}]}